ferm-nftables (1.0.0~1772011348+trixie) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Parses ferm syntax and generates iptables-nftables commands
  * Supports tables, chains, targets, protocols, addresses, ports
  * Compatible with iptables-restore format
  * Includes systemd service
  * Implements --interactive/--timeout for safe rollbacks

